%C3%A2y-s%C6%A1n/poem-uLf8UWeTO8hABErWs9fqVA">Tây sơn - 西山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Kh%C3%B4i/author-VyoW6crCpYZhVl_XKNi3Hw">Lưu Đại Khôi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Thanh-H%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-k%C3%BD/poem-4T3tCDz0kElUt1cfxT71ww">Thanh Hư động ký - 清虛洞記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/T%C6%B0-Dung-h%E1%BA%A3i-m%C3%B4n-l%E1%BB%AF-th%E1%BB%A9/poem-2VDEG5pm4SGWT-o0if2D6g">Tư Dung hải môn lữ thứ - 思容海門旅次</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-S%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-bT4GIPnEJSxYYBPIGRxl0g">Xích Bích đồ - 赤壁圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-S%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-xomLzH62F_NkzLMPyZ81UA">Ngô Sư Đạo</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
